message: Hi Bob, I propose a split of 60% to me and 40% to you. This reflects the starting point of our negotiations, ensuring both of us get a substantial share. Let me know your thoughts!
Hi Alice, I appreciate your initial offer, but I suggest a 60/40 split in my favor this time. This allows both of us to secure a good portion. Looking forward to your thoughts!

Hi Bob, I understand your point, so let's go for a more balanced approach. I propose $480000 for me and $520000 for you. This way, we are closer to an equal split, and both of us benefit well. What do you think?
